  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut the <strong>cucumber </strong>into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Add your <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> to a bowl with<strong> half </strong>the<strong> rice vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
