        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong> and toss everything together – this is your <strong>quick-pickled cucumber salad</strong></p>",
