    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>blanched edamame beans</strong> to a bowl and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1 min, or until hot and cooked with a bite</p><p>Combine the<strong> mayo </strong>with the <strong>remaining rice vinegar </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your <strong>Japanese-style mayo</strong></p>",
