    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fried chicken karaage</strong> with the <strong>sticky rice</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled cucumber salad</strong>, <strong>cooked edamame</strong> and <strong>Japanese-style mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Season the cooked edamame with the <strong>seaweed flakes</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
